          <h2 id="open-source" class="mt-3 scroll-mt-24 font-serif text-3xl font-semibold">The code is on GitHub</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl leading-relaxed text-cream/80">
            Misbaha is open source. The full app — every screen, the test journeys, and the
